# Rule hierarchy

**Edit `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` or `.cursor/skills/` first.** Mirror index lines only in `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, `.antigravityrules`, and other tool stubs (`.cursorrules`, `.clinerules`, `.windsurfrules`).

| Layer | Path | Role |
|-------|------|------|
| Rules | `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` | **Primary** — conventions by glob |
| Skills | `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` | **Workflows** — step-by-step tasks |
| Index | `AGENTS.md` | Entry map (no duplicate rules) |
| Stack | `techstack.md` | Versions, infra, routes, SEO inventory (human reference) |
| Content SEO | `.antigravityrules` | E-E-A-T, engagement, copy |
| Urdu allowlist | `CLAUDE.md` § Urdu | Full allow/deny table |

